txt.en: Foes can be found at the Gnawbone Pit in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat wargs at the Gnawbone Pit.
The wargs of Gnawbone Pit should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Defeat wargs at the Gnawbone Pit
Foes can be found at the Gnawbone Pit in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat wargs at the Gnawbone Pit.
The warg dens of Gnawbone Pit are a dangerous place within the Wildwood. Defeating wargs here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
